<section class="mb-8 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] sm:gap-x-6 sm:items-center">
  <h4 class="font-mono text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-purple-300 dark:text-purple-400 mb-1.5 sm:m-0 text-left">
    Rules
  </h4>
  <ul class="flex flex-wrap list-none gap-y-1.5 gap-x-[22px] text-[13px] text-purple-400 dark:text-purple-300 m-0 p-0">
    <li>Winner is the person who rides the most days in <%= @competition.period_display %></li>
    <li>Ties are broken by total distance</li>
    <li>
      You have to ride at least
      <span class="unit-imperial"><%= daily_distance_miles %> miles</span>
      <span class="unit-metric hidden"><%= daily_distance_km %> km</span>
      in a day for it to count
    </li>
    <li>Activities that count: <%= activity_types_display %></li>
    <li>First place gets to chose what's for dinner, second and last place have to cook</li>
  </ul>
</section>
